# NOTE: the trained model (model/*.pkl), FAISS index (data/*.index,
# data/*.pkl), cleaned datasets (data/*.csv), WHO source PDFs
# (data/who_corpus/*.pdf), and docs PDF are committed
# on purpose so the app runs immediately after cloning:
#   streamlit run app.py
# Rebuild artifacts with:
#   python data/prepare_data.py
#   python model/train.py
#   python data/build_who_corpus.py
